; Coverage for xact.cc (failed assertion in auto_xact)
; When an auto transaction's assert expression evaluates to false,
; a parse error is thrown.

= Expenses
    assert amount < 0
    (Budget)    -1

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 11:
While applying automated transaction from "$FILE", lines 5-7:
> = Expenses
>     assert amount < 0
>     (Budget)    -1
While extending transaction from "$FILE", lines 9-11:
> 2024/01/01 Test
>     Expenses:Food    $10.00
>     Assets:Cash
Error: Transaction assertion failed: (amount < {0})
end test
